                <mxCell id="legend" value="Use cases mapped:&#xa;1) On-Shelf Availability — Mobile/Cameras → Functions + AI Vision/AML → Cosmos → Power BI&#xa;2) Lost Sales &amp; Refill Tracking — Detection events → Lakehouse (OOS duration, lost-sales calc) → Power BI&#xa;3) Job Assignment &amp; Closure — Functions → Service Bus → Logic Apps → SQL → Associate app (before/after photos)&#xa;4) Product Location &amp; Compliance — Image + Planogram diff in Functions/AML → flags in Cosmos/SQL → Power BI&#xa;5) Computer Vision — Mobile uploads + live camera feed both ingress via Front Door → API Management → App Service → Blob/Event Hubs → Stream Analytics / Functions → AI Vision / Custom Vision / AML.&#xa;6) Reporting — Microsoft Fabric (OneLake, Lakehouse, Notebooks, Power BI). No IoT Hub / IoT Edge required for MVP." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=#666666;fillColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=1;fontSize=11;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6" parent="1" vertex="1">
